<TITLE>Shrimp Fettuccine Fusion</TITLE>

<METADATA>
	<SERVINGS>3</SERVINGS>
</METADATA>

<COOKWARE>
	<LARGE POT/>
    <STRAINER/>
</COOKWARE>

<INGREDIENTS>
	<1>
        <CREAM OF CHICKEN SOUP>
            <CAN>0.5</CAN>
        </CREAM OF CHICKEN SOUP>

        <GREEN BEANS>
            <FRENCH STYLE GREEN BEANS>
                <CAN>1</CAN>
            </FRENCH STYLE GREEN BEANS>
        </GREEN BEANS>

        <PASTA>
            <LONG PASTA>
                <FETTUCCINE>
                    <LB>1</LB>
                </FETTUCCINE>
            </LONG PASTA>
        </PASTA>

        <ROTEL>
            <CAN>0.5</CAN>
        </ROTEL>

		<SHRIMP>
			<OZ>12</OZ>
		</SHRIMP>
		
		<VELVEETA>
            <OZ>4</OZ>
        </VELVEETA>
	</1>
	
	<2>
		<BUTTER>
            <TBSP>3</TBSP>
        </BUTTER>

        <GARLIC>
            <MINCED GARLIC>
                <CLOVE>3</CLOVE>
            </MINCED GARLIC>
        </GARLIC>

        <MILK>
            <CUP>0.5</CUP>
        </MILK>
	</2>
		
	<3>
        <LEMON JUICE>
            <TBSP>1</TBSP>
        </LEMON JUICE>

        <PARSLEY>
            <CUP>0.5</CUP>
        </PARSLEY>

        <PEPPER>
            <TBSP>1</TBSP>
        </PEPPER>
	</3>
</INGREDIENTS>

<INSTRUCTIONS>
    <1>
        (a) Bring 3-4 quarts of water to a roilling boil for each pound of <PASTA/> in <LARGE POT/>. Add <PASTA/> and return to boil. Boil uncovered 12 minutes. Drain in <STRAINER/>. (b) Separate <BUTTER/>. (c) Separate <GARLIC/>. (d) Separate <CREAM OF CHICKEN SOUP/>, <VELVEETA/>, <MILK/>, and <PEPPER/>. (e) Separate <ROTEL/>, <LEMON JUICE/>, and <SHRIMP/>. (f) Separate <GREEN BEANS/> and <PARSLEY/>.
    </1>

    <2>
        In <LARGE POT/>, melt <BUTTER/> over medium heat. Add <GARLIC/> and cook 1 minute.
    </2>

    <3>
        Stir in <CREAM OF CHICKEN SOUP/>, <VELVEETA/>, <MILK/>, and <PEPPER/>. Cook over high heat and stir until cheese is melted and mixture is smooth.
    </3>

    <4>
        Stir in <ROTEL/>, <LEMON JUICE/>, and <SHRIMP/>. Cook over medium heat until <SHRIMP/> are pink and opaque, about 4 minutes.
    </4>

    <5>
        Stir in <GREEN BEANS/> and <PARSLEY/> and toss.
    </5>
</INSTRUCTIONS>